65
00:04:33,440 --> 00:04:35,640
<font color=#FFFF00>Hey, kau gila?</font>

66
00:04:41,910 --> 00:04:45,650
<font color=#FFFF00>Kepala, aku sudah mencari kasus serupa.</font>

67
00:04:46,480 --> 00:04:48,990
<font color=#FFFF00>Seminggu sebelum insiden pertama,</font>

68
00:04:49,120 --> 00:04:51,920
<font color=#FFFF00>ada insiden penyerangan serupa.</font>

69
00:04:51,960 --> 00:04:54,080
<font color=#FFFF00>Korban Park Ji Sun, 28 tahun.</font>

70
00:04:54,080 --> 00:04:57,360
<font color=#FFFF00>Pada saat itu, dia sedang bekerja di panti pijat.</font>

71
00:04:57,530 --> 00:05:00,980
<font color=#FFFF00>Setelah dia menolak pria yang mencoba
