83
00:05:30,900 --> 00:05:34,370
<font color=#FFFF00>Itu berarti polanya mungkin berkembang.</font>

84
00:05:34,600 --> 00:05:37,050
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku harus temui korban.
Hubungi dia.</font>

85
