104
00:06:57,720 --> 00:07:01,340
<font color=#FFFF00>Setelah insiden, Park Ji Sun jarang keluar rumah.</font>

105
00:07:01,340 --> 00:07:03,810
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia didiagnosa menderita PTSD,</font>

106
