122
00:08:17,500 --> 00:08:18,860
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku sempat ragu.</font>

123
00:08:20,060 --> 00:08:21,330
<font color=#FFFF00>Itu bukan...</font>

124
00:08:22,800 --> 00:08:25,340
<font color=#FFFF00>...tempat yang normal.</font>

125
00:08:28,910 --> 00:08:30,370
<font color=#FFFF00>Saat aku berdiri di sana,</font>

126
