<font color=#FFFF00>kupikir dia mungkin saja membiarkanku pergi.</font>

138
00:09:45,180 --> 00:09:46,850
<font color=#FFFF00>Entahlah.</font>

139
00:09:47,020 --> 00:09:50,190
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa ada alasan khusus kau berpikir begitu?</font>

140
00:09:50,390 --> 00:09:52,220
<font color=#FFFF00>Entahlah, tapi...</font>

141
