<font color=#FFFF00>Tak ada yang istimewa.</font>

157
00:11:00,420 --> 00:11:02,660
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku sudah memberitahukan polisi.</font>

158
00:11:02,830 --> 00:11:04,160
<font color=#FFFF00>Tak apa.</font>

159
00:11:04,460 --> 00:11:07,470
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau bisa beritahu kami apa pun yang kau ingat.</font>

160
