<font color=#FFFF00>Dia memakai jaket usang.</font>

162
00:11:21,350 --> 00:11:23,350
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku melihat banyak kotoran di sepatu ketsnya.</font>

163
00:11:29,120 --> 00:11:32,360
<font color=#FFFF00>Kupikir dia juga gagap.</font>

164
00:11:32,520 --> 00:11:34,460
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku juga mencium bau alkohol.</font>

165
00:11:35,790 --> 00:11:38,200
<font color=#FFFF00>Tangannya memegang sesuatu,</font>

166
00:11:39,060 --> 00:11:41,030
<font color=#FFFF00>dan dia terus mengutak-atik itu.</font>

167
00:11:43,570 --> 00:11:46,270
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau ingat benda apa itu?</font>

168
00:11:47,270 --> 00:11:49,110
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku belum pernah lihat itu.</font>

169
00:11:51,910 --> 00:11:53,510
<font color=#FFFF00>Itu seperti batu.</font>

170
00:11:53,880 --> 00:11:58,580
<font color=#FFFF00>Itu runcing. Mirip peluru.</font>

171
00:11:59,980 --> 00:12:01,650
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tak begitu yakin,</font>

172
00:12:02,690 --> 00:12:03,950
<font color=#FFFF00>tapi kupikir...</font>

173
